org.apache.taverna.scufl2.xml.t2flow.jaxb

Class Processor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.taverna.scufl2.xml.t2flow.jaxb.Processor

  • public class Processor
extends Object
    A processor of a dataflow. A processor is a dataflow unit that receives input to its input ports, iterates over it using the iteration strategy stack, and pushes it down the dispatch stack to reach the activities that invokes the actual services. The outputs from the services buble up through the dispatch stack and is pushed out on the output ports, indexed according to the iteration strategy.
